One thing I did know
was that from now on,

41:18.970 --> 41:22.099
it would be up to me
to host family dinners.

41:22.140 --> 41:23.801
Don't get me wrong,
one awkward evening

41:23.840 --> 41:25.205
where my dad got drunk

41:25.250 --> 41:27.605
and called my mom and Poppy
scissor sisters three times

41:27.650 --> 41:30.119
doesn't mean
everything's okay.

41:30.150 --> 41:33.245
That's what they call 'em.
Scissor sisters.

41:35.560 --> 41:40.726
Still for the first time since
I found out I wasn't dying...

41:40.760 --> 41:43.798
I was truly happy
to be alive.

